<br>
I can confirm that both High Priest I'Xar and Vazern Ith'Salar or whatever his last name is both drop the imbued night ember sphere. I spent three hours trying to get one of them single. They are somehow linked to the other dragoons so when i thought i had a nice clean tag i would suddenly get a 941 point harm touch from the general and see 2-3 goons running after me at sow speed.<br>
<br>
The trick is to wait until they all start wandering around killing things. I was forced to zone the second time and when i came back i found Vazern wandering with a dragoon. I was surprised to find Vazern at only half life. I waited for them to walk in opposite directions and when Vazern was alone i quickly killed him.<br>
<br>
Tracker would be very very very very very useful or someone who can feign death for this part of the quest.<br>
<br>
I popped it in the solvent of preservation from Xjari and got the new thing. The solvent container was not consumed so im going to try a combine later on in it. <br>
<br>
Here is where i got lost.<br>
<br>
I turned in the sphere to Izera but i only got one powdered night ember back. Has this happened to everyone? I had plenty of slots she just only gave me one.<br>
<br>
I spent the last two hours killing in CC but i havent got the crystallized web silk yet which is required for the first combine.<br>
<br>
